## Enrichment Reports

KEGG pathway enrichment was performed separately for upregulated and downregulated
DEGs using DAVID Bioinformatics (v2023). Gene symbols were submitted against a
Homo sapiens background at EASE threshold 0.05. A total of 10 KEGG pathways were
identified: 8 from upregulated DEGs (5 FDR-significant) and 2 from downregulated
DEGs (nominally significant). Results are stored in 04_DAVID_KEGG/ as raw DAVID
chart report CSVs and a combined summary file. Visualizations (bar chart, bubble
plot, combined figure) are in 05_KEGG_plots/.
